  <h1>Bespoke Services</h1>
  <p>All the products we install will be tailored to your exact requirements. If you want something out of the ordinary we can help — with over 25 years' experience we can install virtually any electrical or electronic device into a vehicle.</p>
  <p>We can undertake wiring loom repairs or modifications to road or race cars, we can add extra interior and exterior lighting to cars, vans and motor homes. We can supply efficient LED lighting solutions for vans and commercial vehicles (working lights inside and out and hi vis warning lights). We can supply, fit and repair electric windows and central locking and can convert key operated central locking into remote controlled systems. We can install a cruise control system to most makes that operates exactly as a factory fitted system with OE quality. We can hard wire your own accessories such as Dash cams and sat navs.</p>
  <p>We can alter the electrical systems in your vehicle to operate as you want them to.</p>
